These covers are available in two main types: flexible covers (TPU) and hard covers (PC), giving you multiple options depending on your needs. Some prefer flexible covers for easy installation and removal, while others prefer hard covers for their high durability.
Ease of use: The back plastic covers feature a smart design that provides easy access to all phone ports and buttons. It has precise openings, allowing you to use the phone to its full functionality without having to remove the cover. Many covers also come with an anti-slip design that provides a firm grip and prevents the phone from slipping off various surfaces.
If you are looking for extra protection for your mobile phone without sacrificing style, a plastic back cover is the ideal choice.
